targets.rawSql:
select 
$__unixEpochTo() AS time, 
IL,
Enlem,
Boylam,
10 as value
from [dbo].[WH_ST_DIM_ILLER] 
where IL='KONYA'
GROUP BY IL,Enlem,Boylam

SELECT
  $__unixEpochTo() AS time,
  count(1) as value,
	KUSAK as metric
FROM [dbo].[BI_PERSONEL]
GROUP BY KUSAK

select
  $__unixEpochTo() AS time,
  count(1) as value,
  ISNULL([STATU],'N/A') as metic  
FROM  [dbo].[BI_PERSONEL]
 group by [STATU]

SELECT
  $__unixEpochTo() AS time,
  count(1) as value,
  cast(ISNULL(IIF(LEN([MEDENI_DURUM])=0,'N/A',[MEDENI_DURUM]),'N/A') as nvarchar(max)) as metric
FROM
 [dbo].[BI_PERSONEL]
GROUP BY ISNULL(IIF(LEN([MEDENI_DURUM])=0,'N/A',[MEDENI_DURUM]),'N/A')

SELECT
  $__unixEpochTo() AS time,
  count(1) as value,
  cast(ISNULL(CINSIYET,'N/A')  as nvarchar(max)) as metric
FROM
 [dbo].[BI_PERSONEL]
WHERE
1=1
AND ((LEN(CONCAT($Unvan,''))=0) OR UNVAN IN ($Unvan))
--AND ((LEN(CONCAT($Bolum,''))=0) OR BOLUM IN ($Bolum))
AND ((LEN(CONCAT($OGRENIM_DURUMU,''))=0) OR OGRENIM_DURUMU IN ($OGRENIM_DURUMU))
GROUP BY CINSIYET

SELECT top 5
  $__unixEpochTo() AS time,
  count(1) as value,
  cast(ISNULL([UNVAN],'N/A') as nvarchar(max)) as metric
FROM
 [dbo].[BI_PERSONEL]
GROUP BY UNVAN
order by 2 desc

select 
$__unixEpochTo() AS time,
t.range as metric,
count(1) as value from (
  select case  
	when KIDEM between 0 and 1 then '00-01'
    when KIDEM between 1 and 5 then '01-05'
	when KIDEM between 5 and 10 then '05-10'
    when KIDEM between 10 and 15 then '10-15'
	when KIDEM between 15 and 30 then '15-30'
    else '30+' end as range
   from [dbo].[BI_PERSONEL]) t
   group by t.range
   order by 2

select 
$__unixEpochTo() AS time,
YAS_GRUBU as metric,
count(1) as value  
from [dbo].[BI_PERSONEL] 
group by YAS_GRUBU

select 
  $__unixEpochTo() AS time,
  count(1) as value, ISNULL([POZISYON],'N/A') as metric  FROM  [dbo].[BI_PERSONEL]
 group by [POZISYON] 
 order by 2 desc

select AVG(YAS) as 'Ortalama Yas' from
BI_PERSONEL

SELECT
  count(SICIL) as 'Personel Sayısı'
FROM
  BI_PERSONEL

SELECT
  $__unixEpochTo() AS time,
  count(1) as value,
  cast(ISNULL(IIF(LEN([OGRENIM_DURUMU])=0,'N/A',[OGRENIM_DURUMU]),'N/A') as nvarchar(max)) as metric
FROM
 [dbo].[BI_PERSONEL]
GROUP BY ISNULL(IIF(LEN([OGRENIM_DURUMU])=0,'N/A',[OGRENIM_DURUMU]),'N/A')
order by metric

SELECT
  $__unixEpochTo() AS time,
  count(1) as value,
  cast(ISNULL(IIF(LEN([KANGRUBU])=0,'N/A',[KANGRUBU]),'N/A') as nvarchar(max)) as metric
FROM
 [dbo].[BI_PERSONEL]
GROUP BY ISNULL(IIF(LEN([KANGRUBU])=0,'N/A',[KANGRUBU]),'N/A')
order by 3

SELECT
 $__unixEpochTo() AS time,
  count(1) as value,
  cast(ISNULL([BOLUM],'N/A') as nvarchar(max)) as metric
FROM
 [dbo].[BI_PERSONEL]
GROUP BY [BOLUM]
